    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> use the consistent attributeName for parameter instead of facetName\n\nNot sure about this one, we need to discuss it first I feel.\n\n`facetName` was chosen for all widgets doing **faceting** while attributeName is more for numeric filters. It's only a way to map our users mind to the information they will find in the algolia dashboard (refinement list requirement: use attributes for faceting).\n\nStill, we can change it maybe but it needs to be in another issue/discussion/PR I think.\n",
